{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_1999-12-22",
 "title": "SW1 Log: An Interview with Poguala",
 "summary": "In the VIP Lounge, the elegant Representative Poguala Waaris-Dawntreader receives the pilot Bazil for a probing, high-stakes interview about a position with the Diplomatic Corps. Over glasses of water, the refined diplomat presses Bazil on his humble, hardscrabble origins and his killing of his slave-owner father, challenging his self-control, his morality, and his readiness. Bazil defends himself with impassioned talk of fighting for freedom, but Poguala coolly dismantles his reasoning, demanding non-violent solutions he could have pursued to free his enslaved mother. Concluding that he is, however justified, a thug and a murderer redeemed only by his X-wing, she bluntly refuses to accept him into her branch of the Diplomatic Corps.",
